data.text:
Jia Nefu

Janev is from Guangdong. He is good at calligraphy and painting, and is good at writing ink on pines, flowers, birds, bamboos and stones, and his pen and ink are green and refined. The calligraphy is plump and handsome. He once served as company secretary of Galaxy Newspapers in Hong Kong. Author of "Collection of Calligraphy and Paintings by Janav".

Yuan Shikai

Yuan Shikai(1859-1916), courtesy name is Weiting, art names are Rongan and Xinxintingzhuren, was born in Xiangcheng, Henan. A prominent politician, military artist, and Beiyang Clique in modern China. He is called Yuan Shikai because of the name of the place where he was born.
